# Fabriq BackUper - git ignore rules
#
# Per-deployment app migration list. The committed sample
# (app_migration_list.sample.csv) is the operator template; the actual
# project-specific file is created by copying the sample and editing it
# in the field, so we intentionally exclude it from git to avoid
# accidentally committing project-confidential application names.
backuper/data/app_migration_list.csv

# Per-satellite extended hostlist (t-0011). The committed sample
# (extended_hostlist.sample.csv) is the template; the live file is created in
# the field and holds ENCRYPTED UNC passwords (ENC:), so it must never be
# committed.
backuper/data/extended_hostlist.csv

# Filled bulk-import staging CSV (may contain PLAINTEXT passwords). Only the
# committed template extended_hostlist_import.sample.csv is tracked.
backuper/data/extended_hostlist_import.csv

# Build artifacts
*.pdb

# Backup output (operator data, never committed)
Backup/
backuper/Backup/

# Temporary / scratch
*.tmp
*.bak
~*
